snippet.description:

At midday in the African savanna, a hyena dares to attack a leopard cub. But the leopard won’t let nature’s thief succeed. A fierce showdown erupts — claws, teeth, and pure survival instinct. Witness the dramatic battle as the leopard fights to protect her cub, turning the tables on the hyena in a breathtaking display of power and determination. This is raw wildlife, where every second counts.
